       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           I D E N T I F I C A T I O N   D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
      * PROGRAM NAME
      ******************************************************************
       PROGRAM-ID. COB05000.
      ******************************************************************
      *                                                                *
      *     ACTUALIZAÇĂO CONTRAVALORES DOS EVENTOS DO ERP              *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
      * Descriçăo da funcionalidade                                    *
      * actualiza contravalores dos eventos do ERP                     *
      ******************************************************************
      *           L O G     D E     A L T E R A C O E S                *
      ******************************************************************
      *  INICIO  * AUTOR  * FIM    *  C O M E N T A R I O S            *
      *          *        *        *                                   *
      *          *        *        *                                   *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           E N V I R O N M E N T         D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                     CONFIGURATION SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-AS400.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-AS400.
       SPECIAL-NAMES.
           DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
      ******************************************************************
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                      INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE-CONTROL.
      ******************************************************************
       DATA DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   D A T A   D I V I S I O N                    *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                          FILE SECTION                          *
      ******************************************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER              PIC X(40) VALUE 'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE'.

       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PGMNAME               PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'COB05000'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME              PIC  X(10)  VALUE 'COB05000'.

      ******************************************************************
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE EXCD0100 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE EXCD0200 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3606 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5005 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6401 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5402 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5502 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5301 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0103 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD0604 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6700 END-EXEC.

      ******************************************************************
      * CONSTANTES
      ******************************************************************
       01  CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-DESC      PIC X(35) VALUE
              'FACTURAS POR EMITIR                '.
           05 CON-COVT3602             PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT3602'.
           05 CON-COVT5005             PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT5005'.
           05 CON-COVT6401             PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT6401'.
           05 CON-COVT5402             PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT5402'.
           05 CON-COVT5502             PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT5502'.
           05 CON-COVT0604             PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT0604'.
           05 CON-COVT6700             PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT6700'.
           05 CON-TO                   PIC  X(03) VALUE 'TO'.
           05 CON-CC                   PIC  X(03) VALUE 'CC'.
           05 CON-BC                   PIC  X(03) VALUE 'BC'.
           05 CON-FACTNEMIT            PIC  X(09) VALUE 'FACTNEMIT'.

      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-DATA-MIN              PIC X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-HOJE             PIC X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-IND                   PIC 9.
           05 WS-ENDERECO              PIC X(03)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CTO                   PIC X(200) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CCC                   PIC X(200) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-BCC                   PIC X(200) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-RCODE                 PIC S9(01) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-T                     PIC S9(12)V9(2) COMP-3
                                                       VALUE ZEROS.

           05 WS-GNOME                 PIC  X(060) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-MOE-INI               PIC X(03) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-MOE-OUT               PIC 9(03) VALUE SPACES.

       01  WS-SWITCHES.
           05 WS-STATUS-COT50       PIC S9(03) VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT50-OK                   VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT50O-NOTFND              VALUE 100.

           05 WS-STATUS-COT64       PIC S9(03) VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT64-OK                   VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT64O-NOTFND              VALUE 100.

           05 WS-STATUS-COT06       PIC S9(03) VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT06-OK                   VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT06O-NOTFND              VALUE 100.

           05 WS-STATUS-COT36       PIC S9(03) VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT36-OK                   VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT36O-NOTFND              VALUE 100.

           05 WS-STATUS-COT67       PIC S9(03) VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT67-OK                   VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT67O-NOTFND              VALUE 100.

      ******************************************************************
      * COPYS
      ******************************************************************
       COPY ATCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY AQCL0001.
       COPY AQCW0109.
       COPY AQCW0009.
       COPY VIAW0030.
       COPY VIAW0012.
       COPY VIATK001.
       COPY VIATK002.
       COPY EXCK0002.
       COPY ETCL0050.
       COPY EXCL0200.

      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 FILLER                     PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT50 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT
                       NIDPROJECTO
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , DDATAEMISS
                     , DDATAEMIS2
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTAXAMOUNT
                     , CMOEDA
                     , NTOTCTRV
                     , NTAXCTRV
                  FROM COVT5005_INVOICES
                  WHERE NTOTCTRV = 0
                    AND (NTOTALAMOUNT <> 0
                     OR  NTAXAMOUNT   <> 0)
              ORDER BY CMOEDA
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , NIDPROJECTO
                     , NIDINVOICE
              FOR UPDATE OF
                       NTOTCTRV
                     , NTAXCTRV
           END-EXEC.
      *
      * COVT6401_INVPAY
      *
           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT64 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT
                       NIDPROJECTO
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , DDATAEMISS
                     , DDATAEMIS2
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTAXAMOUNT
                     , CMOEDA
                     , NTOTCTRV
                     , NTAXCTRV
                  FROM COVT6401_INVPAY
                  WHERE NTOTCTRV = 0
                    AND (NTOTALAMOUNT <> 0
                     OR  NTAXAMOUNT   <> 0)
              ORDER BY CMOEDA
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , NIDPROJECTO
                     , NIDINVOICE
              FOR UPDATE OF
                       NTOTCTRV
                     , NTAXCTRV
           END-EXEC.
      *
      * COVT0604_OPPORTUNITIES
      *
           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT06 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT
                       NVALOR
                     , DALTSTAT
                     , CMOEDA
                     , MCTRVLR
                  FROM COVT0604_OPPORTUNITIES
                  WHERE MCTRVLR   = 0
              ORDER BY CMOEDA
                     , DALTSTAT
              FOR UPDATE OF
                       MCTRVLR
           END-EXEC.

      *
      * COVT3607_PROJECTS
      *
           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT36 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT
                       NIDPROJECTO
                     , CMOEDA
                     , DBEGINDATE
                     , NBUDGET
                     , NBUDCTRV
                  FROM COVT3606_PROJECTS
                  WHERE NBUDGET    <> 0
              ORDER BY CMOEDA
                     , DBEGINDATE
              FOR UPDATE OF
                       NBUDCTRV
           END-EXEC.

      *
      * COVT6700_EXPENSES
      *
           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT67 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT
                       NIDPROJECTO
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , DDATAEMISS
                     , DDATAEMIS2
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTAXAMOUNT
                     , CMOEDA
                     , NTOTCTRV
                     , NTAXCTRV
                  FROM COVT6700_EXPENSES
                  WHERE NTOTCTRV = 0
                    AND (NTOTALAMOUNT <> 0
                     OR  NTAXAMOUNT   <> 0)
              ORDER BY CMOEDA
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , NIDPROJECTO
                     , NIDINVOICE
              FOR UPDATE OF
                       NTOTCTRV
                     , NTAXCTRV
           END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COB05000         '.
      *****************************************************************
      *                    LINKAGE SECTION
      *****************************************************************
       COPY VIAL0005.

      ******************************************************************
      *              P R O C E D U R E   D I V I S I O N               *
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0014 END-EXEC.

       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-FACTURAS
                 THRU 2000-PROC-FACTURAS-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-MOVIM
                 THRU 2000-PROC-MOVIM-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-OPORTUNID
                 THRU 2000-PROC-OPORTUNID-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROJECTOS
                 THRU 2000-PROC-PROJECTOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-DESP
                 THRU 2000-PROC-DESP-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0000-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           GOBACK.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   INICIO PROGRAMA
      ******************************************************************
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           INITIALIZE WS-VARIAVEIS
                    , WS-SWITCHES.

           MOVE ARCK0002-RCODE-OK         TO ATCK0001-RCODE.

      * INFORMA ARQUITECTURA BATCH
           PERFORM AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ
              THRU AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ-EXIT.

           MOVE AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG         TO VIAL0015-I-DEBUG.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-INICIO
                 THRU AQCP0100-REG-INICIO-EXIT
           END-IF.

       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   PROCESSA FACTURAS
      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-FACTURAS.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-FACTURAS   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2100-OPEN-CURCOT50
              THRU 2100-OPEN-CURCOT50-EXIT.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURCOT50
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURCOT50-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT50
              THRU 2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT50-EXIT
             UNTIL NOT ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
                OR NOT WS-COT50-OK.

           PERFORM 2500-CLOSE-CURCOT50
              THRU 2500-CLOSE-CURCOT50-EXIT.

       2000-PROC-FACTURAS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   PROCESSA MOVIMENTOS
      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-MOVIM.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-MOVIM   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2100-OPEN-CURCOT64
              THRU 2100-OPEN-CURCOT64-EXIT.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURCOT64
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURCOT64-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT64
              THRU 2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT64-EXIT
             UNTIL NOT ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
                OR NOT WS-COT64-OK.

           PERFORM 2500-CLOSE-CURCOT64
              THRU 2500-CLOSE-CURCOT64-EXIT.

       2000-PROC-MOVIM-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   PROCESSA OPORTUNIDADES
      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-OPORTUNID.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-OPORTUNID  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCK0002-CSITU-PERDIDA TO COCD0604-CSITUACAO
           PERFORM 2100-OPEN-CURCOT06
              THRU 2100-OPEN-CURCOT06-EXIT.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURCOT06
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURCOT06-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT06
              THRU 2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT06-EXIT
             UNTIL NOT ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
                OR NOT WS-COT06-OK.

           PERFORM 2500-CLOSE-CURCOT06
              THRU 2500-CLOSE-CURCOT06-EXIT.

       2000-PROC-OPORTUNID-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   PROCESSA PROJECTOS
      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-PROJECTOS.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROJECTOS  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2100-OPEN-CURCOT36
              THRU 2100-OPEN-CURCOT36-EXIT.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURCOT36
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURCOT36-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT36
              THRU 2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT36-EXIT
             UNTIL NOT ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
                OR NOT WS-COT36-OK.

           PERFORM 2500-CLOSE-CURCOT36
              THRU 2500-CLOSE-CURCOT36-EXIT.

       2000-PROC-PROJECTOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   PROCESSA DESPESAS
      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-DESP.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-DESP   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2100-OPEN-CURCOT67
              THRU 2100-OPEN-CURCOT67-EXIT.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURCOT67
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURCOT67-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT67
              THRU 2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT67-EXIT
             UNTIL NOT ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
                OR NOT WS-COT67-OK.

           PERFORM 2500-CLOSE-CURCOT67
              THRU 2500-CLOSE-CURCOT67-EXIT.

       2000-PROC-DESP-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   OPEN CURCOT50
      ******************************************************************
       2100-OPEN-CURCOT50.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OPEN-CURCOT50      ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                OPEN CURCOT50
           END-EXEC.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           MOVE SQLCODE                     TO WS-STATUS-COT50.

           IF  NOT DB2-OK
           AND NOT DB2-NOTFND
             SET  VIAW0030-DB2-ERROR         TO TRUE
             SET  VIAW0012-ABEND-DB2         TO TRUE
             MOVE WS-PROGNAME                TO VIAW0030-PGMNAME
             MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID         TO VIAW0030-PARAGRAPH-NAME
             MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME        TO VIAW0030-TABLE-NAME
             MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE           TO VIAW0030-SQLCODE
             MOVE SPACES                     TO VIAW0030-ACCESS-KEY
             MOVE 'ERRO NO OPEN DO CURSOR'   TO VIAW0030-DESC1
             MOVE 'CURCOT50'                 TO VIAW0030-DESC2
             PERFORM VIAP0030-ESCREVE-SPOOL
                THRU VIAP0030-ESCREVE-SPOOL-EXIT
             PERFORM 9990-ABEND
                THRU 9999-ABEND-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2100-OPEN-CURCOT50-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   FETCH CURCOT50
      ******************************************************************
       2200-FETCH-CURCOT50.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-FETCH-CURCOT50  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               FETCH CURCOT50
               INTO :COCD5005-NIDPROJECTO
                  , :COCD5005-GCLIENTE
                  , :COCD5005-DDATAEMISS
                  , :COCD5005-DDATAEMIS2
                  , :COCD5005-NTOTALAMOUNT
                  , :COCD5005-NTAXAMOUNT
                  , :COCD5005-CMOEDA
                  , :COCD5005-NTOTCTRV
                  , :COCD5005-NTAXCTRV
           END-EXEC.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           MOVE SQLCODE                TO WS-STATUS-COT50.

           IF  NOT DB2-OK
           AND NOT DB2-NOTFND
             SET  VIAW0030-DB2-ERROR          TO TRUE
             SET  VIAW0012-ABEND-DB2          TO TRUE
             MOVE WS-PROGNAME                 TO VIAW0030-PGMNAME
             MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID          TO VIAW0030-PARAGRAPH-NAME
             MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME         TO VIAW0030-TABLE-NAME
             MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE            TO VIAW0030-SQLCODE
             MOVE SPACES                      TO VIAW0030-ACCESS-KEY
             MOVE 'ERRO NO FETCH DO CURSOR'   TO VIAW0030-DESC1
             MOVE 'CURCOT50'                  TO VIAW0030-DESC2
             PERFORM VIAP0030-ESCREVE-SPOOL
                THRU VIAP0030-ESCREVE-SPOOL-EXIT
             PERFORM 9990-ABEND
                THRU 9999-ABEND-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2200-FETCH-CURCOT50-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   PROCESSA CURCOT50.
      ******************************************************************
       2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT50.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT50  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2400-TRATA-CURCOT50
              THRU 2400-TRATA-CURCOT50-EXIT.

           IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURCOT50
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURCOT50-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2300-PROCESSA-CURCOT50-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   TRATA CURCOT50
      ******************************************************************
       2400-TRATA-CURCOT50.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2400-TRATA-CURCOT50     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE EXCL0200-DATA    REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                         ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES.

             IF COCD5005-DDATAEMIS2 = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE COCD5005-CMOEDA        TO EXCL0200-EXMOEDORIG
               MOVE AQCW0100-AT-CMOE       TO EXCL0200-EXMOEDDEST
               MOVE AQCW0100-AT-DTOP       TO EXCL0200-EXDATA
               MOVE ZEROES                 TO EXCL0200-EXHORA
               MOVE EXCK0002-CAMB-COMERC   TO EXCL0200-EXTIPOCAMB

               PERFORM 2420-OBTEM-CAMBIO
                  THRU 2420-OBTEM-CAMBIO-EXIT

               IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
                 PERFORM 2435-ACT-CTRVLR
                    THRU 2435-ACT-CTRVLR-EXIT
               END-IF

             ELSE
               MOVE COCD5005-CMOEDA        TO EXCL0200-EXMOEDORIG
               MOVE AQCW0100-AT-CMOE       TO EXCL0200-EXMOEDDEST

               MOVE COCD5005-DDATAEMIS2     TO AQCW0005-DTX10
               PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
                  THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT
               MOVE AQCW0005-DT98          TO EXCL0200-EXDATA

               MOVE ZEROES                 TO EXCL0200-EXHORA
               MOVE EXCK0002-CAMB-COMERC   TO EXCL0200-EXTIPOCAMB

               PERFORM 2420-OBTEM-CAMBIO
                  THRU 2420-OBTEM-CAMBIO-EXIT

               IF ATCK0001-SEM-ERROS
                 PERFORM 2435-ACT-CTRVLR
                    THRU 2435-ACT-CTRVLR-EXIT
               END-IF

             END-IF.

       2400-TRATA-CURCOT50-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   OBTEM CAMBIO
      ******************************************************************
       2420-OBTEM-CAMBIO.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2420-OBTEM-CAMBIO   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

            PERFORM CALL-EXR00200
               THRU CALL-EXR00200-EXIT.

            IF ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              CONTINUE
            ELSE
              SET ATCK0001-ABEND TO TRUE
            END-IF.

       2420-OBTEM-CAMBIO-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   ACTUALIZA CONTRAVALOR
      ******************************************************************
       2435-ACT-CTRVLR.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2435-ACT-CTRVLR     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           COMPUTE COCD5005-NTOTCTRV = COCD5005-NTOTALAMOUNT *
                   EXCL0200-EXVALOR1

           COMPUTE COCD5005-NTAXCTRV = COCD5005-NTAXAMOUNT *
                   EXCL0200-EXVALOR1

           EXEC SQL
             UPDATE COVT5005_INVOICES
                SET NTOTCTRV =   :COCD5005-NTOTCTRV
                  , NTAXCTRV =   :COCD5005-NTAXCTRV
              WHERE CURRENT OF CURCOT50
           END-EXEC.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
             WHEN DB2-OK
               CONTINUE
             WHEN OTHER
               PERFORM 9990-ABEND
                  THRU 9999-ABEND-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.
      *
       2435-ACT-CTRVLR-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   CLOSE CURCOT50
      ******************************************************************
       2500-CLOSE-CURCOT50.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-CLOSE-CURCOT50     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                CLOSE CURCOT50
           END-EXEC.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF  NOT DB2-OK
           AND NOT DB2-NOTFND
             SET  VIAW0030-DB2-ERROR         TO TRUE
             SET  VIAW0012-ABEND-DB2         TO TRUE
             MOVE WS-PROGNAME                TO VIAW0030-PGMNAME
             MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID         TO VIAW0030-PARAGRAPH-NAME
             MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME        TO VIAW0030-TABLE-NAME
             MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE           TO VIAW0030-SQLCODE
             MOVE SPACES                     TO VIAW0030-ACCESS-KEY
             MOVE 'ERRO NO CLOSE DO CURSOR'  TO VIAW0030-DESC1
             MOVE 'CURCOT50'                 TO VIAW0030-DESC2
             PERFORM VIAP0030-ESCREVE-SPOOL
                THRU VIAP0030-ESCREVE-SPOOL-EXIT
             PERFORM 9990-ABEND
                THRU 9999-ABEND-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2500-CLOSE-CURCOT50-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   OPEN CURCOT64
      ******************************************************************
       2100-OPEN-CURCOT64.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OPEN-CURCOT64      ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                OPEN CURCOT64
           END-EXEC.

